data.description: If you are looking for a nice size backyard in a great neighborhood, this could be the place for you! Nicely maintained 3 bedroom 2.5 Bath Colonial with a 2-car garage on a beautiful lot.  Walk into this charming home with Living Room with plenty of windows and natural light, the a separate Dining Room with hardwood floors, to the Kitchen with all Stainless appliance, gas stove cooking, granite counters and plenty of spaces for your cooking needs.  Full size laundry room on the main level and well placed Half Bath too.  Family Room off Kitchen has hardwood floors, Vaulted Ceilings, wood burning fireplace with decretive mantel.  Sliding glass door to the back tiered deck and over look this expansive backyard!  Swing & shed convey! Primary Bedroom upstairs is of good size, with walk-in closet, vanity, and private Bathroom with large Shower and some nice updates.  Bedroom #2 & #3 of good size with wood style laminate flooring. Conveniently located Hall Bath has tub/shower.  Basement has a Large finished Rec Room and an unfinished area that can fit most storage needs (also rough in for bathroom plumbing).  Recent updates include - Freshly painted, newly carpeted, New Windows, New Front Door, and New Fencing.  Shed, playground, Nest Thermostat, & Ring doorbell all convey.
